➜一汽终于如愿！正面抢广丰汉兰达饭碗，更强动力版“汉兰达”明年上线
http://www.sohu.com/a/437287968_99994080	52233
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201209/0580fc2c01644bbc99d1c71eb841c0e7.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201209/da0432ca3723420583fcf25409d6dc73.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p><strong>本文编辑：</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201209/10c1d40ddf17424f87eb266cb5b7a896.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p><strong>写在前面：</strong></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
